thread.title_full: Alpha Flight Guru reviewed by Liz

author: Liz
title: Liz
text:
Joe kept me up to date on what flights were available, I gave him the dates we wanted to fly and a Quote: from another agent. He managed to find a better flight at a better price. He kept in phone contact and advised of the alternatives.
We are yet to take the trip, but are very happy with the previous service we have had from Australia to USA east coast on Cathay Pacific.
Thank You Joe
